<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
        <style>
            h1 { font-size: 40px; }
            h2 { font-size: 30px; }
            p  { font-size: 14px; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>
            We came across your website <strong>${domain}</strong> and we think it would be
            a great fit for our link-building platform, <strong>Slinky Linky</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
            We connect content marketers with quality website owners like yourself. As a
            Supplier on our platform, you would receive paid article placement requests
            directly — no cold outreach, no chasing.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you're interested, please click <a href="${responseUrl}">here</a> to find
            out more and register your interest. You can also upload a list of other sites
            you manage, or share a link to a Google Doc with your site portfolio.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you'd rather not hear from us again, you can decline on the same page and
            we'll remove you from our list.
        </p>
        <p>Any questions, feel free to get in touch.</p>
        <p>Regards,</p>
        <p>
            <em>${signoff}</em><br/>
            <em>${signoffContactDetails}</em>
        </p>
        <img src="cid:logo-cid" width="53px" style="float:left"/>
        <h1 style="float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-top:0px">Slinky Linky</h1>
    </body>
</html>
